trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid.PageIndexChanged"></xref> event of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid.PageIndexChanged"> </xref> hendelse av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid.PageIndexChanged> event is raised when a button in the page selection element of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> control is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid.PageIndexChanged>denne hendelsen oppstår når en knapp i sideelementet for valg av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid>kontrollen klikkes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid.PageIndexChanged>

trans-unit.source: For a list of initial property values for an instance of DataGridPageChangedEventArgs, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: En liste med opprinnelige verdier for en forekomst av DataGridPageChangedEventArgs, kan du se den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about handling events, see [NIB: Events and Delegates](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d98fd58b-fa4f-4598-8378-addf4355a115).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om behandling av hendelser [NIB: hendelser og representanter](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d98fd58b-fa4f-4598-8378-addf4355a115).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create and initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å opprette og starte en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: When an instance of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridCommandEventArgs> is created by a call to this constructor, the following properties are initialized to the specified values.
trans-unit.target: Når en forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridCommandEventArgs>er opprettet av et kall til denne konstruktøren følgende egenskaper blir initialisert til de angitte verdiene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridCommandEventArgs>

| Egenskaper | Standardverdi | |----------------|-------------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs.CommandSource%2A>| Den `commandSource` parameteren. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs.NewPageIndex%2A>| Den `newPageIndex` parameteren. |</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs.NewPageIndex%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridPageChangedEventArgs.CommandSource%2A>

trans-unit.source: The index of the page selected by the user from the page selection element of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for siden som er valgt av brukeren fra sideelementet for valg av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the source of the command.
Use the CommandSource property to determine the source of the command that raised the event.
trans-unit.target: Bruk CommandSource-egenskapen til å fastsette kilden for kommandoen som hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: Because this event is raised only when a button in the page selection element of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> control is clicked, the returned source is a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem> object that represents the page selection element.
trans-unit.target: Fordi denne hendelsen oppstår når en knapp i sideelementet for valg av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid>kontrollen klikkes, returnerte source er en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem>objektet som representerer utvalget sideelementet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGridItem> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid>

trans-unit.source: Gets the index of the page selected by the user in the page selection element of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter indeksen for siden valgte av brukeren i sideelementet for valg av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Use the NewPageIndex property to determine the index of the page selected by the user in the page selection element of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> control.
trans-unit.target: Bruk NewPageIndex-egenskapen til å fastslå indeksen for siden valgte av brukeren i sideelementet for valg av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid>

trans-unit.source: This value is often used to set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid.CurrentPageIndex%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> control to display the selected page.
trans-unit.target: Denne verdien er ofte brukes til å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid.CurrentPageIndex%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid>kontrollen til å vise den valgte siden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid.CurrentPageIndex%2A>

trans-unit.source: The index of the page selected by the user in the page selection element of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for siden valgte av brukeren i sideelementet for valg av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid"> </xref> kontrollen.
